Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.84,0:10:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,真火大
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.24,0:10:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,真是超讓人討厭的味道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.59,0:10:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,好臭 在鼻子周圍揮之不去的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.88,0:10:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,太令人討厭了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.48,0:10:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,看我打飛你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.40,0:10:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,神樂！真是個不知隱忍的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.19,0:10:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我說阿波羅 你怎麼隨隨便便就打起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.88,0:10:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,說也沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.54,0:10:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,輕鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.83,0:10:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.43,0:11:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.61,0:11:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.65,0:11:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡 像只瘋狗一樣亂竄
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.52,0:11:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,和你一模一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.04,0:11:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.76,0:11:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,遲鈍的女人！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.60,0:11:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,有一手…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.88,0:12:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.65,0:12:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,有人？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.73,0:12:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Jin君…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.93,0:12:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.68,0:12:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.72,0:12:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,柚葉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.67,0:12:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,快住手啊 無口女
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.98,0:12:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,柚葉的Bio-wave已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.14,0:12:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Element Change
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.76,0:12:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,御子乃去和柚葉交換
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.23,0:12:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,柚葉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.49,0:12:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Jin君…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.98,0:12:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Jin？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.53,0:13:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事吧 婕希卡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.53,0:13:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣下去會沒完沒了的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.34,0:13:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我們上 御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.68,0:13:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.93,0:13:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Aquarion Gepada
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.24,0:13:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你這傢伙 擅自就…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.38,0:13:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你就在一邊乖乖坐著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.33,0:13:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,既然你不肯消停的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.85,0:13:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,成功了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.89,0:13:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,誰知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.41,0:14:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,再多讓我樂一樂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.39,0:14:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,柚乃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.20,0:14:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,關於這本書…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.97,0:14:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,不要過來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.96,0:14:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不要過來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.21,0:14:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,柚乃 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.88,0:14:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,剛才的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.50,0:14:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,信君
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.41,0:14:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 快起來啊 臭女人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.40,0:14:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Element Change
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.98,0:14:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,阿馬塔去交換婕希卡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.30,0:15:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,阿馬塔君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.07,0:15:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,御子乃 剛才那個…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.41,0:15:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,作為補償 這周週日…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.84,0:15:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我們一起 去約會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.80,0:15:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.86,0:15:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不 那樣就好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.94,0:15:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,去吧 阿馬塔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.04,0:15:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.16,0:15:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.13,0:15:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你以為這樣就能得到我的原諒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.57,0:15:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼這樣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.47,0:15:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,夠了 少給我整天發情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.80,0:15:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,臭女人的仇 由我來報
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.10,0:15:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,信君 剛才那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.49,0:15:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,好多汗 不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.54,0:16:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,柚乃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.10,0:16:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,柚乃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.20,0:16:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,信君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.66,0:16:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,不要得寸進尺了 你這條臭狗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.04,0:17:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,青蛙之子將會夢見森羅萬象嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.29,0:17:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,而在夢境的前方 所注視的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.41,0:17:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,又是何方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.29,0:17:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.32,0:17:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.75,0:17:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你醒過來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.55,0:17:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你們 難道是機械天使的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.68,0:17:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,看來我們是超越了次元斷層
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.88,0:17:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,被送到了另一個次元來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.53,0:17:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,那這裡…是裂隙對面的世界？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.12,0:17:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.85,0:17:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,總覺得 我好像在哪裡見過你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.13,0:18:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Jin
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.48,0:18:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,不對 原來如此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.87,0:18:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.21,0:18:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我說 這個難道是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.22,0:18:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,創世之書？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.87,0:18:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,信君
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.66,0:18:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.85,0:18:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,這個氣味…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.89,0:18:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,就是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.02,0:18:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.95,0:18:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.21,0:18:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.57,0:18:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,恐怕正是因為這本創世之書被分成了兩半
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.05,0:18:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,才引起了這次的空間扭曲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.00,0:19:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,本來一樣東西分裂成兩樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.94,0:19:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不同的兩個世界重疊在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.56,0:19:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,真是太麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.15,0:19:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,三色堇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.16,0:19:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,是一種花語為「請不要讓我孤身一人」的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.32,0:19:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,非常怕寂寞的花呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.81,0:19:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,孤身一人？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.49,0:19:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,那個人對你很重要嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.37,0:19:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,還不是很明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.11,0:19:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,但在一起的時候就是會很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.06,0:19:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,但是…我…實在太膽小了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.93,0:19:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,有些時候還會莫名其妙的感到悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.80,0:19:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有任何的預兆…突然的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.90,0:19:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺像是被非常重要的人拋棄了一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.70,0:19:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,就像那種遙遠過去的記憶甦醒了一般
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.14,0:19:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,所以奪走這本書…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.04,0:19:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,對我來說就像奪走了重要的朋友一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.05,0:19:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我根本沒有好好去聽信君所說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.09,0:20:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你很像我一個朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.94,0:20:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,非常的溫柔 是個非常堅強的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.77,0:20:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.14,0:20:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.82,0:20:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,次元斷層在不斷的擴大
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.60,0:20:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼辦好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.10,0:20:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,只要讓書恢復原樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.21,0:20:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,世界也應該能一起恢復的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.00,0:20:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 必須想辦法去那對面才行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.74,0:20:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼請帶我一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.36,0:20:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我把一個女孩子弄哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.27,0:20:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,做了很過分的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.50,0:20:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 我必須去道歉才行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.84,0:20:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,和我一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.64,0:20:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.44,0:20:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,誒 我說等等
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.84,0:20:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,有什麼不好的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.35,0:20:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼率直 真的很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.39,0:20:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 我不管了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.04,0:21:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,柚乃 一定會讓你回到原來的世界的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.65,0:21:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我們來幫你
Comment: 0,0:21:10.74,0:21:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,IN
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.60,0:21:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你們兩人 把力量借給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.17,0:21:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.23,0:21:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,真沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.05,0:21:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,混成合體
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.67,0:21:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Aquarion Spadion
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.28,0:21:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我們上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.34,0:21:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,混成合體
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.77,0:21:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Aquarion Gepaion
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.47,0:21:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,請不要讓我孤身一人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.94,0:21:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.40,0:21:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你一直…獨自一人…在那裡哭泣著
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.53,0:21:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,但是…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.72,0:21:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,柚乃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.67,0:21:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我…已經不想再看到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.31,0:21:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你的眼淚了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.59,0:22:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我也想…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.36,0:22:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,再一次見到信君
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.18,0:22:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我不會再讓你孤身一人了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.09,0:22:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是 一定要好好的傳達到
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.00,0:22:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.99,0:22:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,阿馬塔君
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.52,0:22:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我能聽到…你的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.82,0:22:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,傳達到御子乃那裡去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.55,0:22:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,傳達到阿馬塔君那裡去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.46,0:22:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,孤獨畢業彈
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.92,0:23:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,顯示器還沒辦法恢復嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.79,0:23:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,到底發生了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.14,0:23:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,誒 小玉 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.78,0:23:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,不成嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.97,0:23:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我是不會放棄的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.59,0:23:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,柚乃 我一定會到達你那裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.69,0:23:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,信君…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.31,0:23:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,什！是誰擅自就！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.14,0:23:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,小玉！？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.09,0:23:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.24,0:23:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,發生了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.64,0:23:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,等下 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.24,0:23:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.32,0:23:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.97,0:24:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.46,0:24:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,青春合體
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.17,0:24:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,GO
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.28,0:24:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Aquarion！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.50,0:24:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 這個感覺是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.25,0:24:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,非常的溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.07,0:24:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,太舒服了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.60,0:24:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼？青蛙？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.52,0:24:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯 青蛙
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.43,0:24:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,回去…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.25,0:24:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,回去…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.22,0:24:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,大家一起回去
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.32,0:24:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.32,0:24:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.72,0:24:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,歸宿之地
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.39,0:24:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,超歸還合體
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.62,0:24:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Go！Aquarion！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.70,0:24:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,那 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.97,0:24:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,真是兩個麻煩的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.87,0:24:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,御子乃 真的非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.62,0:24:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我才是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.88,0:25:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.78,0:25:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.05,0:25:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,命運紅線拳
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.78,0:25:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,撐不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.24,0:25:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,信 柚乃 拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.20,0:26:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,無限跳躍
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.92,0:26:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,創世之書…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.06,0:26:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我們有緣再見吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.34,0:26:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.84,0:27:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Jin君
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.78,0:27:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,那個 書的事情…真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.64,0:27:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事 已經沒關係了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.74,0:27:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我已經找到了 我一直在尋找的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.95,0:27:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.04,0:27:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.14,0:27:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,請不要再哭泣了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.98,0:02:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.62,0:28:17.11,INJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}世界の始まりの日　生命(いのち)の樹の下で
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.26,0:28:23.66,INJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}くじらたちの声の遠い残響　二人で聞いた
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.66,0:28:29.68,INJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}失くしたものすべて　愛したものすべて
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.14,0:28:36.60,INJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}この手に抱きしめて　現在(いま)は何処(どこ)を彷徨(さまよ)い行くの
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.74,0:28:41.78,INJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}答えの潜む琥珀の太陽
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.88,0:28:48.84,INJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}出会わなければ　殺戮の天使でいられた
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.39,0:28:54.44,INJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}不死なる瞬き持つ魂
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.91,0:28:58.13,INJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}傷つかないで　僕の羽根
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.28,0:29:05.14,INJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}この気持ち知るため生まれてきた
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.33,0:29:11.27,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}一万年と二千年前から愛してる
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.56,0:29:17.76,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}八千年過ぎた頃からもっと恋しくなった
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.02,0:29:23.89,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}一億と二千年あとも愛してる
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.28,0:29:32.48,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}君を知ったその日から僕の地獄に音楽は絶えない
